Class CookieList

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<Cookie>
        • com.krobothsoftware.commons.network.value.CookieList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Cookie>, Collection<Cookie>, List<Cookie>, RandomAccess

    public class CookieList
extends AbstractList<Cookie>
implements RandomAccess, Cloneable, Serializable
    ArrayList of Cookies with put methods. Methods put(Cookie) and putAll(Collection) will remove dublicate and add new one.
    Since:
    SNC 1.0
